Package: python3-aiohttp-openmetrics
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Architecture: all
Description: OpenMetrics provider for aiohttp
 This project contains a simple middleware and /metrics route endpoint
 for aiohttp that allow easy implementation of the openmetrics
 protocol.
 .
 At the moment, this package is a thin wrapper around the
 prometheus_client package.
 .
  from aiohttp import web from aiohttp_openmetrics import metrics,
 metrics_middleware
 .
 app = web.Application() app.middlewares.append(metrics_middlware)
 app.router.add_get('/metrics', metrics)
 .
 web.run_app(app)
